task.summary:
Long field headland mode #2577 and #2333
Course for long and narrow fields. Under the hood it generates headland rows only until they cover the entire field, but on the short edge of the field every row except the outermost one has zero offset.
Works fine for rectangular fields, may not be very pretty for odd shaped ones but there this mode doesn't really make sense anyway.
Set turn radius in headland corners.
Set turn radius in headland corners.

#2635 fixed starting position when no headland.
Trying to make @pops64 happy...

Fix for multiple islands.
Was only generating headland path for the first island found. Now all islands will be circled.
Skip rows fixed for multi-block fields
First usable two side headland version

#2884 last or first up/down row overlaps headland
Instead of the adjacent row to reduce the likelihood of collisions when multiple vehicles are on the course.
New fieldwork patterns work in progress.
Pathfinder refactoring, code cleanup and documentation
6.01.00206 attempt to improve headland -> up/down row transition #3598

6.01.00215 Racetrack pattern fix
Need to work with a copy of the headland path waypoints in the a*star algorithm as we set the onCloseList property on them...

6.01.00217 Course generator improvements for #3250 #3760
Racetrack pattern updated to start in the middle, skipping 4 rows and work in multiple chunks.

6.01.239 Racetrack/spiral pattern improvements #3958
Pathfinding does not cut corners on headland.

6.01.00261 Fitness calculation improved in genetic algorithm #4041
Fitness values were rounded so for very large fields we always ended up with 0 which prevented the selection from working.
Initialize fitness to -1 and use the floating point value, no rounding.
Also increased the maximum number of blocks to 30 so odd shaped fields like 10 and 24 at Kandelin will take forever to generate but eventually they will finish.

Added analytic expansion to hybrid A*
For now, just the Dubins path
New pattern and some pathfinder performance improvements
Fix transition from headland to up/down for lands pattern
No headland lane switch near corners
